          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service=\"frontend\"} | kind=\"api-timing\" | json | status=\"0\" [$__range]))",
          "queryType": "instant"
        }
      ],
      "description": "The fetch rejected outright: offline, DNS, CORS or aborted. Completely invisible to the backend, and the reason this panel exists \u2014 in an app that queues events offline, a call that never landed can mean a recorded action the server never saw."
    },
